00:05:29.798 --> 00:05:31.158
Want to dismantle my mansion?

00:05:31.478 --> 00:05:32.158
I was foolish

00:05:32.798 --> 00:05:34.877
and failed your concern for my father.

00:05:35.637 --> 00:05:37.317
