00:05:37.598 --> 00:05:38.798
yet I failed to be alert

00:05:39.197 --> 00:05:40.757
and got my father poisoned by villains,

00:05:40.957 --> 00:05:41.918
with his life in danger.

00:05:42.408 --> 00:05:43.877
I'm here to beg for the antidote.

00:05:44.136 --> 00:05:46.358
Please help us.

00:05:48.678 --> 00:05:50.077
Lord Dingyuan has been poisoned?

00:05:51.397 --> 00:05:51.838
Yes.

