00:06:11.038 --> 00:06:13.077
I can't stand idle.

00:06:14.440 --> 00:06:15.358
But you know what?

00:06:16.437 --> 00:06:18.397
Deadly Poison is a peculiar poison.

00:06:19.598 --> 00:06:20.957
Let's be honest,

00:06:22.517 --> 00:06:24.238
Lord Dingyuan

00:06:24.478 --> 00:06:25.877
crossed the line and did wrong

00:06:26.278 --> 00:06:29.278
at the prince's incident a decade ago.

00:06:29.918 --> 00:06:30.798
I bet he's

00:06:32.118 --> 00:06:33.397
targeted by someone.

00:06:34.437 --> 00:06:36.478
I can save him now,

00:06:36.877 --> 00:06:38.678
not forever.

00:06:41.118 --> 00:06:42.478
If you offer help,

00:06:42.718 --> 00:06:44.678
the Xue family will remember this grace.

00:06:45.480 --> 00:06:46.757
If you want to ask questions,

00:06:47.437 --> 00:06:48.397
I can give you answers

00:06:48.877 --> 00:06:50.718
after my father's recovery.

00:06:51.478 --> 00:06:52.317
Please wait

00:06:53.118 --> 00:06:53.877
for a few days.

00:06:54.317 --> 00:06:55.557
You want

00:06:56.798 --> 00:06:59.358
to take my antidote today,

00:07:00.118 --> 00:07:01.557
yet make me wait days

00:07:01.718 --> 00:07:03.278
for answers?

00:07:04.077 --> 00:07:05.158
I beg for your mercy.

00:07:11.757 --> 00:07:12.197
Right.

00:07:12.957 --> 00:07:14.997
Do you possess

00:07:14.997 --> 00:07:16.678
a portrait of the late empress?

00:07:17.397 --> 00:07:18.637
Give it to me,

00:07:19.238 --> 00:07:20.838
and I'll give you the antidote.

00:07:22.158 --> 00:07:23.317
(Why do they all want that?)

00:07:26.358 --> 00:07:26.838
Okay.

00:07:26.997 --> 00:07:27.798
The painting

00:07:28.757 --> 00:07:29.478
for the antidote.

00:07:30.184 --> 00:07:30.637
Go.

00:07:39.238 --> 00:07:41.118
Lord Dingyuan has been poisoned?

00:07:44.200 --> 00:07:45.877
Lord Dingyuan has been poisoned.

00:07:46.077 --> 00:07:47.877
Lord Dingyuan has been poisoned.

00:07:50.792 --> 00:07:52.118
Nuannuan, here.

00:08:08.158 --> 00:08:09.077
What to do, Hexu?

