Her hands grow colder.

00:08:10.997 --> 00:08:11.557
Start a fire.

00:08:11.918 --> 00:08:12.358
Got it.

00:08:23.877 --> 00:08:24.278
Alright.

00:08:25.278 --> 00:08:25.757
I'm here.

00:08:27.278 --> 00:08:28.077
So cold.

00:08:29.238 --> 00:08:29.957
So cold.

00:08:41.198 --> 00:08:41.718
(Ms. Wang,)

00:08:42.397 --> 00:08:42.997
(hang on.)

00:08:43.997 --> 00:08:44.558
(Hang on.)

00:08:47.157 --> 00:08:47.718
(Ms. Wang,)

00:08:48.677 --> 00:08:49.718
(you'll recover soon.)

00:08:53.637 --> 00:08:54.517
(Why be so silly?)

00:08:56.478 --> 00:08:58.198
(What matters more than life?)

00:08:59.037 --> 00:08:59.997
(Why took the poison?)

00:09:01.438 --> 00:09:02.677
(What are you hiding?)

00:09:10.078 --> 00:09:11.318
Why do you live

00:09:12.558 --> 00:09:13.757
such a difficult life?

00:09:21.677 --> 00:09:23.637
I still found sweetness in such moments.

00:09:24.238 --> 00:09:25.438
I'm truly heartless.

00:09:31.958 --> 00:09:33.718
Hexu, is she alright now?

00:09:52.078 --> 00:09:52.877
Young Master,

00:09:53.757 --> 00:09:54.517
don't go.

00:10:11.958 --> 00:10:12.598
Get out.

00:10:34.917 --> 00:10:35.438
I...

00:10:38.037 --> 00:10:38.877
I didn't die.

00:10:40.438 --> 00:10:41.958
Hexu begged for the antidote.

00:10:44.157 --> 00:10:45.997
(Deadly Poison
belongs to Jing'an Bureau.)

00:10:46.718 --> 00:10:48.358
(Did he go to Grand Tutor Zhou?)

00:10:50.118 --> 00:10:51.877
(How could he leave unscathed?)

00:10:55.318 --> 00:10:55.757
Come on.

00:10:56.078 --> 00:10:57.397
Chicken soup stewed with ginseng.

00:10:57.598 --> 00:10:58.277
Let her drink it.

00:10:58.877 --> 00:10:59.464
Jiaoqian.

00:10:59.797 --> 00:11:02.198
When Dongyang had raging fever,
you didn't use this ginseng.

00:11:02.718 --> 00:11:04.958
Now you've stewed this?

00:11:05.517 --> 00:11:06.637
Why save me?

00:11:07.797 --> 00:11:08.958
I should be dead.

00:11:15.118 --> 00:11:15.917
Everyone out.

00:11:31.358 --> 00:11:32.118
Why do you

00:11:33.238 --> 00:11:34.517
always speak of death?

00:11:35.078 --> 00:11:35.997
Once dead,

00:11:36.318 --> 00:11:37.238
you can do nothing.

00:11:37.997 --> 00:11:39.198
Nosy.

00:11:39.917 --> 00:11:40.958
Those truly wishing to die

00:11:41.558 --> 00:11:43.037
don't struggle for life like you do.

00:11:44.397 --> 00:11:45.478
Your family has gone.

00:11:46.118 --> 00:11:48.198
They wouldn't want you
joining them so soon.

00:11:50.397 --> 00:11:51.558
You know nothing.

00:11:52.277 --> 00:11:52.757
Yes,

00:11:53.438 --> 00:11:54.037
