00:17:40.278 --> 00:17:41.637
and your body turned cold...

00:17:43.758 --> 00:17:44.677
Stop right there.

00:17:45.318 --> 00:17:47.237
If Grand Tutor Zhou discovers

00:17:47.358 --> 00:17:48.877
that you harbor the former Crown...

